Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，那不错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, that's good.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你得知道，说实话，我-我之前还有点担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know, to be honest, I-I was a little worried before.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这听起来很蠢，\N{\fnArial\fs48}This might sound silly,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.01,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我很高兴我能陪你一起长大\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I'm really glad that I'm going to get to grow up with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，到底怎么了？发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, what's going on? What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.82,0:08:27.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们刚才只是在聊天，然后突然间-\N{\fnArial\fs48}We were just talking, then all of a sudden --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他变回婴儿了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}he turned back into a baby?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}伙计，我怎么说的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dude, I told you!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.93,0:08:36.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}将你的身体拉伸这么长时间对你没好处\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stretching your body out for that long is not good for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}给你啦，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here you go, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，不，不，不要把他给我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, no, no, don't give him to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.02,0:08:45.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}把他给我吧，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hand him over, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}接住了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here you go.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的能力对新生儿毫无作用\N{\fnArial\fs48}My power means nothing to an infant.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，这个归我管吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, this is my department.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.66,0:09:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你打算怎么做？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别担心，我能行的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, I got this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石人们怎么会不知所措呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How can the gems not know what to do?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你以为她们了解如何抚养一个宝宝？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You think they knew the first thing about raising a baby?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实一直都是我，但我不知道为什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}That was all me, but I don't get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}开车原来总能让他安静下来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Driving always used to calm him down.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我们该怎么让他变回去？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}But how do we change him back?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.26,0:09:22.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道，听着，康妮，让我带你回家吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know. Look, Connie, let me take you home.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我会在这一切都解决后给你回电话的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I'll call you when this all gets sorted out.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，不\N{\fnArial\fs48}W-wait, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我要留下来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want to stay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.21,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你确定？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.53,0:09:33.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只想在史蒂文身边\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just want to be there for Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别担心，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.31,0:09:39.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不论你多大对我都无所谓\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't matter to me what age it seems like you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只是想和你在一起而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want to hang out with you no matter what.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你爸爸仍然得运营他的洗车房，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your dad still has to run his car wash,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.55,0:09:45.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而宝石人们得去做她们的事，\N{\fnArial\fs48}and the gems have to do gem stuff,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么我会在他们没空时陪你的\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I'll watch you when they're not around.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也可以在与珍珠完成训练后来看你的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can come see you after I'm done training with Pearl, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那听起来有趣吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看看啊-他总算不哭了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at that -- he finally stopped crying.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.35,0:09:58.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}总之，这是个好的开始\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, that's a start.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.77,0:10:00.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么了，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's up, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文宝宝该换尿布了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Baby Steven needs changing.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我的天，哦哦哦，我的天！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my gosh. Ohhh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他变得更小了？史蒂文变成微观物了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Did he get even smaller? Steven's microscopic!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他变回受精卵了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's reverted back to a zygote!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所有人！史蒂文变成-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everyone, Steven is --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.33,0:10:20.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快看，现在合身了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look, it fits now.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你又变回正常了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're back to normal!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真对不起那变成了一场灾难\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry this was a disaster.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我只想为你变得成熟一点\N{\fnArial\fs48}I wanted to look older for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.06,0:10:30.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那无所谓\N{\fnArial\fs48}That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我听到你在面包车里说的话了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I heard what you said in the van.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:33.80,0:10:36.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我不能像人类一样成长的话真的没问题吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's really okay if I don't age like a human?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.22,0:10:38.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然啦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我就是喜欢你这样啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}I like you just the way you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，好吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，史蒂文，你下巴上有东西\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, Steven, you've got something on your cheek.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.86,0:10:47.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是胡子啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Its a facial hair!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.62,0:10:53.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}爸爸！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dad!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是什么，史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What is it, little man?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.57,0:10:55.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的妈，你长胡子了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Holy smokes, you're growing a beard!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你真的在长大！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You really are getting older!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}大家快看这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everybody, look at this!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}难以置信\N{\fnArial\fs48}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}非常有趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}Very impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那里还会长出更多的吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is there more where that came from?
